Waiver one.

02:47:53.917 --> 02:47:54.097
Yep.

02:47:54.978 --> 02:47:55.538
Waiver 01.

02:47:55.978 --> 02:47:57.058
Is there any public comment?

02:47:57.219 --> 02:47:57.959
No public comment.

